== Continuos integration

After developers works on the code, they will push it to git repo, once they pushed build server like jenkins/git immediately takes this code and compiles it like (java --> .class & c++ --> executables) after this it will create a .jar file/.exe or Docker image. this is done by using Maven/Gradle/ANt (build tools) file.

CI goal is to detect issue at early face. so that it does not multiply.

Developers code, automatically build and tested after they commit the code. If this went fine then Artifact/software gets stored in reposities in the form of docker image.

